#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:1
msgid "E4081"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:3
msgid "The identifier is bound more than once in the same pattern."
msgstr "标识符在同一个模式绑定多次。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:5
msgid ""
"It is not possible to bind two values to one identifier because they "
"might have different values. If you want to shadow the first identifier, "
"you can use `_` to discard it."
msgstr "不能将两个值绑定到同一个标识符，因为它们可能具有不同的值。如果想要遮蔽第一个标识符，可以使用 `_` 来丢弃它。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:9
msgid "Erroneous Example"
msgstr "错误示例："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:11
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn f(a : Int?, b : Int?) -> Unit {\n"
"  match (a, b) {\n"
"    (Some(a), Some(a)) => println(\"Some(\\{a})\")\n"
"    _ => println(\"None\")\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:17
msgid "Use a different name for the second identifier."
msgstr "对第二个标识符使用不同的名称。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:19
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn f(a : Int?, b : Int?) -> Unit {\n"
"  match (a, b) {\n"
"    (Some(a), Some(b)) => println(\"Some(\\{a}), Some(\\{b})\")\n"
"    _ => println(\"None\")\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  f(Some(1), Some(2))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:23
msgid ""
"If you want a shadow-like behavior here, you can explicitly discard the "
"first `a` using `_`:"
msgstr "如果你想要类似遮蔽的行为，可以使用 `_` 显式丢弃第一个 `a`："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4081.md:26
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn g(a : Int?, b : Int?) -> Unit {\n"
"  match (a, b) {\n"
"    (Some(_), Some(a)) => println(\"Some(\\{a})\")\n"
"    _ => println(\"None\")\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  g(Some(1), Some(2))\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
